BTC Break Even Calculator App
====

A utility designed to calculate the breakeven point for your Bitcoin transactions. 
It can help minimize losses for Bitcoin traders.

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.CT.BTC_Break_Even_Calculator
====

Changelog
